body:
I run the `tensorflow/tensorflow:0.10.0rc0` and all `list`, `nested list`, `dict` and `tuple` work like a charm. The `dict` works because my local TensorFlow is `0.9.0` and the document seems really clear.

Thanks for your guide @vrv and this feature is really important for our inference services.

BTW, the `tensorflow/tensorflow:latest` is not "latest" at all.
